Package: vfc.3dscatter
Type: Package
Title: A Simple 3D Visualization R Package for Numeric and Ordinal Data
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2023-10-01
Authors@R: c(
    person(given="Vlad-Florin",family="Chelaru",email="vladflorinchelaru@gmail.com",role=c("aut","cre"),comment=c(ORCID="0000-0003-2954-3263"))
  )
Maintainer: Vlad-Florin Chelaru <vladflorinchelaru@gmail.com>
Description: Assuming triplets of ordinal or numeric values, represent them in interactive 3D views.
    This package uses `rgl` to view the data, and also allows the view of the distribution of the data points, on two-by-two axes.
License: GNU GPL 3.0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
  rgl
Imports:
  MASS,
  stringr
